=== Pronunciation ===
[[Category:Hebrew language]]
מראה / mar'eh / mar-eh'
=== Etymology ===

From {{HH|7200}}; 
=== Noun ===
a view (the act of seeing); also an appearance (the thing seen), whether (real) a shape (especially if handsome, comeliness; often plural the looks), or (mental) a vision: -  X apparently, appearance (-reth), X as soon as beautiful (-ly), countenance, fair, favoured, form, goodly, to look (up) on (to), look [-eth], pattern, to see, seem, sight, visage, vision.